{"tid":1261453,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"差佬用緊咩戰術？","createTime":"2019-06-27T08:48:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-27T09:45:56.000Z","uid":261435,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d53d330a951f34a72e3451a66027f7db39f51901","tid":1261453,"uid":261435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T08:48:17.000Z","msg":"我夢見有人講起琴晚警方包圍係用左<span style=\"color: red;\">沸水戰術（Kettling)</span>-係曾偉雄帶入香港架：<br />\n<br />\n//在倫敦2001年的五一勞動節遊行中，近三千名反資本主義的徒手和平示威者，在市中心Oxford Circus旁邊的一條短街被防暴警察圍困了七個小時。有被圍困的示威者表示，警察這樣無預警地把幾千人圍在狹窄的空間之内，長時間<span style=\"color: red;\">斷水斷糧、更沒有厠所，使示威者陷入飢餓、疲倦和極度壓抑的境地</span>；少數想離開包圍圈、同警察理論的示威者，更被打至頭破血流；也有和平無聲地坐在包圍圈内的示威者，被忽然突入的小隊防暴警察擡起、扔向百貨公司的玻璃櫥窗。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最後，防暴警察打開了一個缺口放人，每個示威者都被拍下大頭照，還被侍候在兩旁的警察棒打腳踢。//<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2ZOByov\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2ZOByov&d=F8rBtbRGk5TlA8%2FYPnv0drZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=9ae786b4\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2ZOByov</a><br />\n<br />\n//The term &quot;kettle&quot; is a metaphor, likening the containment of protesters to the containment of heat and steam within a domestic kettle.//<br />\n<br />\n//Kettling has been criticized for being an indiscriminate tactic which leads to the detention of law-abiding citizens and innocent bystanders.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[7] In some cases protesters are reported to have been denied access to food, water and toilet facilities for long periods.[2] Further criticism has been made that in some instances <span style=\"color: red;\">the tactic has been used to foment disorder with the aim of changing the focus of public debate</span>.[8] <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />In some countries the tactic has led to legal challenges on the grounds of human rights violations.//<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kettling\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FKettling&d=F8rBtbRGk5TlA8%2FYPnv0drZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=a5473e51\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kettling</a><br />\n<br />\n即係話，警察咁撚好禮貌，同時激起示威者既憤怒，全部都係公關手段，想<span style=\"color: red;\">扭轉輿論</span>！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n被抄左牌既手足，如果警察遲點call你去協助調查，記得call埋律師，同埋行使緘默權啦,咩都話「我冇野講」就得。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n手機唔使開俾佢架，就算佢有搜查令，最多只可以沒收你電話，等狗拎返去慢慢crack啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37b877e04edcfd285a4190179075e8ef2fe75833","tid":1261453,"uid":24951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T09:10:09.000Z","msg":"推一推先！"},{"pid":"2e7013d946743bec9067174eedccfcbf53b943f3","tid":1261453,"uid":150625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T09:16:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9faa1c166394274aca6a756dccece3f28a6ed392","tid":1261453,"uid":13594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T09:23:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bcc955ceb4eaab2accb05c8d5707a809b4e75f4","tid":1261453,"uid":179379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T09:23:44.000Z","msg":"協助調查唔使理<br />\n有拘捕令就call律師<br />\n<br />\n冇搜查令就唔使開門<br />\n有嘅可以call律師睇住佢搜<br />\n（詳情睇法夢fb）<br />\n<br />\n唔好講任何嘢（狗狗搵你傾計都唔得）<br />\n唔好亂簽紙（簽咗冇得返轉頭）<br />\n唔好信狗"},{"pid":"fcf39116bb20262702b6efb1e6d2e082158cf96c","tid":1261453,"uid":242083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T09:30:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2aa12eb284ec35491bae0b9ffe6a80ffcc061a9a","tid":1261453,"uid":223320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T09:42:21.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推"},{"pid":"79f02fececac4d0084de66e9c04252f19629930b","tid":1261453,"uid":223320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T09:44:39.000Z","msg":"冇入時事台都睇唔到個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0823fd0fa454ec787bcd5f493640ef068fe41c32","tid":1261453,"uid":182061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T09:45:56.000Z","msg":"推下先"}]}